    Class RedisDatabase

    If redis disabled RedisDatabase injected. Aim of this RedisDatabase is not to throw errors when you don't enable redis within your configuration AddRedisPersister(IServiceCollection, IConfiguration) does this accordingly to configuraiton. So DO NOT USE this directly

    This dummy database does nothing, just returns default values
